Wouldn't it be nice to have an official API to search within a span for an array? I could imagine it happens quite often that developers use IndexOf and then look ahead if it matches against an array. At least I do a lot of times. 

```
var bla =  new char[] {'a', 'b', 'c', 'd', 'e'};
var index = bla.AsSpan().IndexOf({ 'b', 'c'});

var bla = new byte[] {0x1, 0x2, 0x3, 0x4, 0x5};
var index = bla.AsSpan().IndexOf( { 0x2, 0x3});
```

Or even more advanced with null-able feature to search with wildcard support?

